## 🌐 Web Enumeration with Gobuster

Run directory brute-forcing against the target:

```bash
sudo gobuster dir -u http://<TARGET_IP>:80 -w /usr/share/wordlists/dirbuster/directory-list-2.3-medium.txt -t 100
```
